{"tid":32152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大亞灣泄漏 第3日始封","createTime":"2016-12-10T04:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T05:58:56.000Z","uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1829e175bf6f1d9b08ac754fa0600a7fb4fb56","tid":32152,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:52:46.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】內地微信公號「中國核能」透露，廣東大亞灣核電站上月底大修期間發生主泵阻尼器泄漏事件，隨後在廣核設計院核島所牽頭下，陝西特種橡膠製品公司承擔封堵項目。該公司在接到任務幾小時內設計出密封方案，並通過國家核安全局批准，2日內完成工裝模具製造、電器控制系統改造、膠圈生產，第3日一行3人將所有封堵工具送往大亞灣基地，密封設備於上周二（11月29日）完成安裝，周日（4日）並網發電。據悉，現場操作環境有放射性。目前，陝西特種橡膠製品公司發布的有關消息已被刪除，大亞灣網站並無披露這一事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161210/s00013/1481308396284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161210%2Fs00013%2F1481308396284&d=ppbbp4CU0VjMx5jr2u2yKXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=333e175e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161210%2Fs00013%2F1481308396284&h=5014c39c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161210/s00013/1481308396284</a>"},{"pid":"2761562d153e65acba70ba3e83bfb232090729ed","tid":32152,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:53:30.000Z","msg":"臭屁大魔王放了一個屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ccb3bdbde4f5d9a8011f5a74d16b825d233f0d4","tid":32152,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人等收皮了"},{"pid":"ff6dab6f85992d2b2af1afca99c0fd804df91ec3","tid":32152,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T04:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【明報專訊】內地微信公號「中國核能」透露，廣東大亞灣核電站上月底大修期間發生主泵阻尼器泄漏事件，隨後在廣核設計院核島所牽頭下，陝西特種橡膠製品公司承擔封堵項目。該公司在接到任務幾小時內設計出密封方案，並通過國家核安全局批准，2日內完成工裝模具製造、電器控制系統改造、膠圈生產，第3日<span style=\"color: red;\">一行3人</span>將所有封堵工具送往大亞灣基地，密封設備於上周二（11月29日）完成安裝，周日（4日）並網發電。據悉，現場操作環境有放射性。目前，陝西特種橡膠製品公司發布的有關消息已被刪除，大亞灣網站並無披露這一事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161210/s00013/1481308396284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161210%2Fs00013%2F1481308396284&d=ppbbp4CU0VjMx5jr2u2yKXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=333e175e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161210%2Fs00013%2F1481308396284&h=5014c39c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161210/s00013/1481308396284</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一行三人RIP得！"},{"pid":"b813971a17e1f8ae61a511d08b5b0ac0ac9dcbbb","tid":32152,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"中央又送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b67bd2e46558b162a0a013d5d9ec0b06e910e48","tid":32152,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"三個死士 應該係俾人呃過去"}]}